This coconut mango sago pudding dessert is an interesting twist on the famous sago pudding which originated in Southeast Asia and has become a very popular dessert in many countries and cultures. Recreate this refreshing and delicious recipe and enjoy it after your Sunday lunch or dinner with your friends and family.  ALSO TRY: Recipe of the day: Quick and easy bacon jam recipe This recipe was found on beyondsweetandsavory.com